         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">7/4/85 ¶  ¶ Just after I addressed and posted a short letter to you, ¶  respected Mr Stephani, the consignment of samples of the Jungermanniaceae that you so kindly named reached me. I am very pleased...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">85.04.07a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Franz Stephani</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Conservatoire et Jardin botanique, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">MS annotation by Stephani: 10/6.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>7/4/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nachdem ich eben ein kurzes Schreiben an Sie richtete u. auf die Post gab, geehrter Herr Stephani, erreicht mich die Sendung der Muster von den Jungermanniaceen, welche Sie gütig benannten. Ich bin recht froh, dass Sie auch doch etwas </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Neues</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> darunter fanden, so dass Sie Ihre Mühe nicht ganz umsonst hatten.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es wäre gut, wenn Sie die neuen Arten bald publiciren, da sonst jemand Ihnen noch mit der Beschreibung dieser Species zuvor kommen könnte. Sie haben mich durch Ihre schnelle Untersuchung der gesandten Sachen recht zum Weitersammeln ermuthigt.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Dankbar Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7/4/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Just after I addressed and posted a short letter to you,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to F. Stephani, 5 April 1885 (in this edition as 85-04-05b).</p>
               </note> respected Mr Stephani, the consignment of samples of the <name key="Jungermanniaceae">Jungermanniaceae</name> that you so kindly named reached me. I am very pleased that you also did find something <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">new</hi>
               </seg> among them, so that your effort was not quite in vain.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It would be good if you published the new species soon, because otherwise someone could anticipate you with the description of this species.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The new species mentioned has not been identified, but see Stephani (1889).</p>
               </note> You have encouraged me very much to further collecting by your rapid investigation of the things sent.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Gratefully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Jungermanniaceae">Jungermanniaceae</name>
            </p>
         </div>
